{"_path":"/maps/_person/technology/andrej-karpathy","_dir":"technology","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Andrej Karpathy","description":"AI 研究员、教育家，OpenAI 创始成员，前 Tesla AI 高级总监","original_path":"content/6.maps/_person/andrej-karpathy.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Andrej Karpathy 是斯洛伐克裔加拿大计算机科学家，1986 年出生于捷克斯洛伐克。他是斯坦福大学李飞飞教授的学生，博士期间专注于深度学习与计算机视觉。Karpathy 是 OpenAI 的创始成员和研究科学家，后担任 Tesla AI 高级总监，领导自动驾驶的计算机视觉团队。2023 年离开 Tesla 后回归 OpenAI，2024 年离职专注于 AI 教育。他被网友称为\"赛博活佛\"，因其将复杂的 AI 概念讲解得深入浅出。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"主要贡献观点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要贡献/观点？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM 科普教育"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"制作了多个面向普通观众的高质量 LLM 科普视频，包括："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《State of GPT》- 详解大模型训练流程（预训练、SFT、RLHF）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《How I use LLM》- 实用的大模型使用指南，涵盖提示技巧、工具选择、生态系统"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神经网络教育框架"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开发了 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/karpathy/micrograd","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"micrograd"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 和 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/karpathy/llm.c","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"llm.c"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 等教学项目，用最精简的代码展示核心原理。llm.c 仅需约 1000 行 C 代码即可训练 GPT-2 级别的语言模型。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对 LLM 本质的理解"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提出 LLM 是\"数据标注员的神经网络模拟\"的观点——监督微调阶段的模型本质上是学习了人类标注员的回复风格。同时强调 LLM 的\"瑞士奶酪\"能力特征：在某些任务上表现惊艳，却在简单任务上有出人意料的盲点。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"强化学习的潜力"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"认为思考型模型（如 o1、o3-mini）通过强化学习在可验证领域（数学、代码）发现的思考策略，可能代表 AI 超越人类水平的新范式，类似 AlphaGo 的\"第37手\"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"代表作品"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代表作品？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bZQun8Y4L2A","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"State of GPT"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (2023) - 微软 Build 大会演讲，详解大模型训练"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EWvNQjAaOHw","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How I use LLM"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (2025) - 实用的大模型使用指南"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/karpathy/llm.c","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"llm.c"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 纯 C 语言实现的大模型训练"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/karpathy/nanoGPT","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"nanoGPT"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 最简洁的 GPT 训练实现"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/@AndrejKarpathy","rel":["nofol